Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Assigned when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Assigned in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Assigned compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Assigned and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned in cases that eventually reach Completed + In Call versus those that end in Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Accepted + Assigned in variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + Assigned and Completed + Resolved when Completed + In Call does not occur in the variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Assigned in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned when preceded by Queued + Awaiting Assignment and followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Time from case start to Accepted + Assigned in variants that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration of Accepted + Assigned relative to the total resolution time of the case when Completed + In Call is present
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time between Accepted + Assigned and Accepted + Wait - Vendor in variants also containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Assigned in variants where it appears more than once before reaching Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
